The SneezyMUD Client is a Windows client that is no longer being actively 
developed, but offers some basic MUD client functions including aliases, 
triggers and a mapper.

The SneezyMUD Windows Client is not supported by the immortals of SneezyMUD,
but questions may be posted to the SneezyMUD forums.

Minimum software requirements:  Windows 98 and Internet Explorer 5.0.  If
you do not meet these requirements, you must download the Microsoft Common
Controls Update, available on the SneezyMUD website.

Download the SneezyMUD client at http://www.sneezymud.com in the Help
section.  You may also download the Microsoft Common Controls Update and
the sounds archive at this page.

